                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6083" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0921</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8286 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">想说爱你不容易：山东黄金跨国并购卡帝诺的艰与险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">It is not easy to say loving you: the difficulties and dangers of Shandong Gold’s cross-border acquisition of Cardino</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈欢，杨美婷，周家琛，孙宁宁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东黄金矿业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东黄金；卡帝诺；跨国并购；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Shandong Gold; Cardino; Cross-border M&amp;A</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近几年，受国际政策波动的影响，黄金的经济地位不断上升。由于矿产资源的稀缺性，黄金公司持续加码，纷纷布局优质资源，国内企业加大跨国并购的步伐。在“走出去”战略下，山东黄金以场外要约方式收购加纳卡帝诺资源有限公司100%股份。但由于政治因素、竞争对手等原因，山东黄金的海外并购之路一波三折。本案例描述了山东黄金所处的宏观背景及公司发展战略规划，再现了山东黄金如何克服不利因素击败竞争对手，多次提价最终斥资29亿元人民币跨境并购卡帝诺公司的全过程。本案例主要用于企业并购等方面的教学工作，通过本案例的学习，旨在帮助学生理解和掌握企业进行海外并购的战略决策因素、并购定价及风险防范等相关知识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, under the influence of international policy fluctuations, the economic status of gold has continued to rise. Due to the scarcity of mineral resources, gold companies continue to increase their size and deploy high-quality resources one after another. Domestic companies are increasing the pace of cross-border mergers and acquisitions. Under the &quot;going global&quot; strategy, Shandong Gold acquired 100% of Ghana Cardino Resources Co., Ltd. shares through an off-market offer. However, due to political factors, competitors and other reasons, Shandong Gold&#39;s overseas mergers and acquisitions have experienced twists and turns. This case describes the macro background of Shandong Gold and the company&#39;s development strategy plan, and reproduces how Shandong Gold overcomes unfavorable factors and defeated its competitors. It raised prices several times and finally spent RMB 2.9 billion in cross-border mergers and acquisitions of Cardinol. This case is mainly used for the teaching of corporate mergers and acquisitions. Through the study of this case, it aims to help students understand and master the strategic decision-making factors of overseas mergers and acquisitions, merger pricing and risk prevention and other related knowledge.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
